claims:
1. A system for producing oil and/or gas comprising:
a mechanism for recovering oil and/or gas from an underground formation, the oil and/or gas comprising one or more sulfur compounds, the mechanism for recovering comprising a well;
a mechanism for converting at least a portion of the sulfur compounds from the recovered oil and/or gas into a carbon disulfide formulation, the mechanism for converting comprising a reactor; and
a mechanism for releasing at least a portion of the carbon disulfide formulation into the formation, the mechanism for releasing comprising a well;
wherein, any oil and/or gas, as present in the underground formation prior to releasing the carbon disulfide formulation, has a sulfur content from 0.5% to 5%.

11. A method for producing oil and/or gas comprising:
recovering oil and/or gas from an underground formation, the oil and/or gas comprising at least one sulfur compound;
converting at least a portion of the sulfur compound from the recovered oil and/or gas into a carbon disulfide formulation; and
releasing at least a portion of the carbon disulfide formulation into the formation;
wherein, any oil and/or gas, as present in the underground formation prior to releasing the carbon disulfide formulation, has a sulfur content from 0.5% to 5%.
